  ::
  ::  if we detect cache inconsistencies, wipe and rebuild
  ++  change-read-status
    |=  [time=@da =index:store read=?]
    ^+  poke-core
    =.  poke-core  (upd-cache read time index)
    =/  tib=(unit timebox:store)
      (get:orm notifications time)
    ?~  tib  poke-core
    =/  not=(unit notification:store)
      (~(get by u.tib) index)
    ?~  not  poke-core
    =?    poke-core
